Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:13.48,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 启程·初雪之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:42.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:06.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那暮羽的爸爸原来是坐坦克的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:07.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:12.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅用六辆米路帕德二式 从被完全包围的瓦丁布克中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:15.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出千名以上的市民和士兵的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:19.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说级的撤退战英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:23.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:30.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 在作战中光荣负伤的爸爸\N与医院卫生员的妈妈邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:36.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 两人的孩子就是小暮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:37.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:42.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你当我是马铃薯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 真是漂亮的马铃薯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多得小彼的悉心照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:54.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也可以分点给镇上的人们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 克劳斯也应该会来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他带点礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:06.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小暮真的很喜欢克劳斯叔叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是喜欢什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是敬仰他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我戳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:37.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 还能吹出这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是梨旺前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起风了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气也快要变坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:03:59.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃也来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:13.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:17.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得梨旺前辈有点奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说那小号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹得真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得她有点闷闷不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:28.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是一直都不说废话的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…对了 晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天妇罗真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:35.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 马铃薯热乎乎的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:36.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 梨旺 趁热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:52.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:54.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:01.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那青椒 大口大口地吃下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那个梨旺前辈竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:11.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 不管是多小的碎末 也绝对会\N半粒不留地找出并挑走的那个梨旺前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:26.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我戳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:29.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是克劳斯叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠之狼 奇迹的克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:48.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左胸纹有象征第481小队的团结与荣誉狼头纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么担心也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:02.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长的时候也是我们自寻苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 是那个梨旺前辈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又酷又帅又漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:17.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 青椒也一定是成功克服 已经可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:21.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小暮 真的很喜欢梨旺前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈可是我的憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小乃认为怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…戳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:38.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃已经睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:56.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿她没办法 我腾出半张床来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 你抬那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:19.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室的火 你忘记熄了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:22.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 刚没留意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:28.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然严肃中又有点松懈的地方是你的亮点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最近放得太松了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:38.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在为挂了父亲的电话而感到后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作上的失误我会帮你纠正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:55.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在她们的面前 像个有型的前辈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风吹的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:09.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜造访 失礼了 一号特急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收领人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:15.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1121小队和宫梨旺军士长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收领
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:31.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 先进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:34.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的天气 今天已经不能走动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是沙漠之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该跟你说过别那样叫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:45.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为表歉意 要喝杯热茶洗洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:52.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台风之中执行任务 辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:57.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这是昨晚的剩菜 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:58.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:07.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯叔叔来了你就叫醒我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷了也一样好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青椒也很用心地照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:21.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我摘是我炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 暮羽将来应该是个好媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新报纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:32.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 少校把这个也一起带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休战协定怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议好像还是难以进展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:40.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件似乎完全没有妥协
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伊莉亚皇女还健在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情应该就不会这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:49.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉亚…皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:52.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:54.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位比嫩兰的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:57.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿基拉亚鲁大公殿下的第一皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我们赫尔维西亚的胜利女神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:04.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比得上沙漠之狼--克劳斯少校的坦克之神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:09.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生紧急事态了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吵什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:44.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美奈那里的孩子早上开始就失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮一帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美奈 是谁不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:53.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是诚也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河水涨了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:12.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下游的田应该还没完成收割
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是水坝垮了的话 什么都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇上的路我不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:19.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我没看好他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救灾也是军队的任务之一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:37.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:38.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:47.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚也 诚也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 水都那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一掉下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:09.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚也！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:17.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有头绪才跑出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚也在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:36.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:39.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美奈姐姐最喜欢吃茄子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:44.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 之前大家用零花钱买来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚也他一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒着这样的台风跑来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话 你个呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都冒着性命出来找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们自己要来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没叫你们来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:33.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你给我适而可止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:40.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有父母的孩子必须比普通的孩子要老实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为给大家添麻烦的话 大家会说你迟早会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是你们 由美奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:56.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的姐姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是孤儿 所以很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:09.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:10.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还嘟嚷什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:21.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悉心培养的东西如同生命般可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长到这么大 是时候可以吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:33.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成咸菜的话 可是非常好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚也开始爬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 请你先上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:15.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不 你先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人总算没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:50.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没有上去的手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:58.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况最糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然情况变坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有少校跟我一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 一定会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 别吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:36.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在跟奇迹的克劳斯在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:37.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面已经撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二次灾害吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 所以我才讨厌小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:51.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听话的小鬼把他绑起来关进黑屋就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨旺！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:55.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能动摇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:59.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们无论何时都看着你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我说太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:07.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不过 一定会有办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯叔叔可是被称作奇迹的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:17.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是沙漠之狼也不是奇迹的克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:22.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧同名还有身材相似
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:28.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见面的时候暮羽自己一厢情愿地认定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯也不太会说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:33.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着该怎么否认 拖拖拉拉的就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:35.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在的问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么把只有军龄够长的通信兵\N和有干劲没经验的二人组从那里救出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把绳子弄过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面没有落脚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果从这边伸出绳子的话 距离又太远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:01.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把绳子弄到那边的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到克劳斯叔叔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想 如果爸爸活着的话 一定是这么威风的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:19.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我跟大家说得我好像很熟悉爸爸似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:23.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 其实也就是听别人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:24.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:29.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂事的时候他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:30.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:58.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意…左上方？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建御雷神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷锚直线发射可用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:20.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁定系统 从B7到F5部份启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缆锚准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:35.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:36.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:47.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来代替你去世的老爸 好好地保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:11.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:25.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小暮！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷起缆锚 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 暮羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:02.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算得救了 我才跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:04.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:05.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台风过后的蓝天…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是演到最后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 我吃大惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到你能做到那个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到她真切地相信我的眼睛后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.15,0:21:39.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得破坏暮羽的幻想比起死更让我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能做出那样的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来 我就是个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:50.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:52.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯叔叔 很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:02.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁人看到的和本人感觉到的 大多情况下是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:07.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着「仰慕」的眼镜 总是让人看不清真实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:10.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到一天有人戴着这副眼镜看你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:12.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就明白其中的痛苦
